剪輯版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/gefdi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fgefdi&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70ur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=c15272e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/gefdi</a><br />\n傷者瘋狂流血<br />\n<br />\n０：１８ 衝入車一刻<br />\n１：５５ 打人後進入車廂狀況<br />\n２：１９ 第二名傷者<br />\n３：４４ 第三名傷者／地下灘血／狂滴血<br />\n６：３５ 第三名傷者訪問"},{"pid":"08118bec7fb951943eef29d5b3b3e17e7e27b355","tid":1524643,"uid":95501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec04ab895204ad6ffdc73a251f7c147df1b2e433","tid":1524643,"uid":192709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"時間緊迫，要靚留返比高手搞，<br />\n唔好自己係連登打飛機, 放上REDDIT，twitter, facebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">音量注意</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/H6D70-guAFQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FH6D70-guAFQ&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70ur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=2c34de87\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/H6D70-guAFQ</a><br />\n<br />\n再利申：海外巴打借AC"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:59:28.000Z","msg":"To people all around the world,<br />\n<br />\nWe, Hongkongers just experienced a terrorist attack planned and executed by our Hong Kong Police Force. At about 10pm today, our police force rushed into our railway system in Prince Edward station, got in to the carriage and indifferently beat up all the people in it regardless they are protesters or simply passengers. They ignored the weapon guidelines and fired tear gas indoor in the carriage which is in fact lethal. Also, they beat up innocent people causing them seriously wounded. Some passengers kneeled before them asking them to stop but the response they got were beaten ever harder. Meanwhile, the police haven&rsquo;t arrested the passengers after they got beaten up, showing that the only purpose of their brutality was to sort their anger to violence but not dispersing the crowd.<br />\n<br />\nWe, Hongkongers are experiencing a humanitarian crisis and we hope that people all over the world can help us in anyways you can think of. Thank you and we will stay strong.<br />\n<br />\nHongkongers<br />\n31/8/2019"},{"pid":"6a54ecd0b50c60c2695886b644880a4a013c9153","tid":1524643,"uid":192709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba3cdf22a97af3dbf4b9ae9816e69f957b445b6","tid":1524643,"uid":192709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bf8e9395ab07877ee55a024619ab6658462292","tid":1524643,"uid":192709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c1997e6e1a0f8ca40ddbb59618918d2f477fbe","tid":1524643,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:00:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6f3e1007d769d55e1310f5d268fdbdbf2e658dc8","tid":1524643,"uid":192709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d68378cd254169f082f0b1a2976f0fb47374203","tid":1524643,"uid":192709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1695d92b75e153a4256de4bd484183fe83f9a4","tid":1524643,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:09:15.000Z","msg":"有無一刀不剪唔係cctvb架？<br />\n聽日可以去機場派文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}